    "• CLUE (Trinh and Le, 2018).",
    "The CLUE dataset consists of 9 NLU Chinese datasets, namely TNEWS, IFLYTEK, CLUEWSC2020, AFQMC, CSL, OCNLI, CMRC 2018, ChID, and C3.",
